ity inspections, providing first-hand evidence of the impact of inspectors' support.&#10;&#10;In summary, while education inspectors have generally improved their support for schools in recent years, there is still a need to strengthen their focus on digital competence and consistently prioritize teaching and learning in schools causing concern.">
