g programs, mentorship opportunities, or donations of materials and equipment.&#10;6. Encourage schools to engage their communities in the funding process: Empower schools to involve local communities in fundraising efforts and decision-making around resource allocation, helping to build a broader base of support for education and ensuring that funds are used in ways that align with community values and priorities.">
